728984f-b.title: Richmond: Hylan Boulevard - Preston Avenue
728984f-b.text:
(1)
4768 Hylan Boulevard, south side, at Preston Avenue, showing
the John Hauee residence, known as the ''Wakefield'' (1898 to 1917 maps).
It was earlier (1874 map) the G.S. Becket house.
June 17, u926
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
A daisy field in rear of the Hales residence. The view is
southward teward Raritan Bay.
June 17, 1926.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(3)
Another view toward the Bay.
June 17, 1926.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
